John now lives in exile and is more determined than ever to find out what happened to his missing sister Camilla. Each track leads him to organized crime in Stockholm, where Jorge is about to strike his final blow: committing the biggest robbery in Swedish history. During the complex preparations he meets Nadia, a woman from his past.
